    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to imperial officers of the ancient Roman empire entrusted with the management of the financial affairs of a province as agents of the emperor.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
